data.description: Lovely REMODELED 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom in the exclusive Brentwood Crossing community! This home in the sought-after neighborhood boasts a FULL FINISHED BASEMENT with NEW paint and NEW flooring. The home rests on a level lot with lots of entertainment spaces. There's a screened-in patio off of the family room for extended living, a patio off of the lower rec room, and a playground for kids or grandkids! Beautiful hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, and newly painted bedrooms. Upgrades also include a $7000 Pergola, a 3D wall design in the dining and living room, and fresh paint on the exterior trim of the house and garage door. Enjoy cooking in the upgraded kitchen with fresh paint and a walk-in pantry. Laundry can be fun with a brand-new state-of-the-art washer and dryer combination with SMART technology! This home also comes with newly installed barn doors, a custom-designed closet in the owner's bedroom in addition to his/her closet, and an amazing owner's bathroom. The community amenities include a resort-style swimming pool with slides, tennis courts, a cabana, and a deck for year-round fun! This is a must-see home. Schedule your tour today! To maintain a sense of community and a residential atmosphere, there are community rental restrictions.
